{"tid":2013233,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鄧炳強：女子報稱警署內遭強姦正被通緝 涉給假口供","createTime":"2020-05-12T07:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T01:01:55.000Z","uid":84308,"like":15,"dislike":98,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"c82cc8b7ddc1a376ea1334eae6cbd929e69f4051","tid":2013233,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:15:10.000Z","msg":"警務處處長鄧炳強出席元朗區議會會議時說，一名外籍人士日前被捕後死亡的事件，同事全部根據規矩工作，暫時看不到有做得不好的地方。鄧炳強回應議員提問時指，該名人士在街上行為失常、打爛東西，警方接報後與兩名途人制服他，由於對方精神異常，因此召喚救護車將他送院後於翌日離世。初步醫療報告顯示，死者沒有骨折，但要詳細檢視驗屍報告才能確定死因，相信會召開死因庭處理。另外，鄧炳強表示，一名女子早前聲稱在警署遭強姦的案件，律政司已指示警方以涉嫌給予假口供拘捕對方，但她目前已經潛逃，正被警方通緝。<br />\n<br />\n2020-05-12 15:05:17<br />\nRTHK"},{"pid":"50b8ba89e5c10c67327277412f8abf3cb31fd989","tid":2013233,"uid":213877,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嬲"},{"pid":"db18b87b63f29c25f490bbcb8d48eb82e7ed1d68","tid":2013233,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:15:53.000Z","msg":"CLS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf52194bb72b0d8b54d40c7fd76b93b722928a04","tid":2013233,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:16:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"23f9e470583393dd049df5669eabb60cfda874af","tid":2013233,"uid":134474,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:16:15.000Z","msg":"CLS<br />\n人哋有埋律師代表醫學報告"},{"pid":"38ef0b26f61f0a790f6cf8cb0af2a4157a3a7255","tid":2013233,"uid":156376,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:16:54.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2545655a58e4fc716b7fbb6ed6c9a8adee3f588","tid":2013233,"uid":40520,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020